how accurate your shooting is.

592
00:37:39,712 --> 00:37:41,811
Jing? Why are you here?

593
00:37:42,450 --> 00:37:43,650
I didn't know you were there.

594
00:37:44,011 --> 00:37:44,811
Are you hurt?

595
