No.

596
00:38:06,771 --> 00:38:07,571
Give it back to you.

597
00:38:23,936 --> 00:38:25,792
Why are you alone?

598
00:38:26,250 --> 00:38:27,531
Aren't you with my sister?

599
00:38:27,730 --> 00:38:28,331
I...

600
00:38:31,690 --> 00:38:33,571
Fangfeng Bei, you tricked me.

601
00:38:34,331 --> 00:38:35,531
It's just a joke.

602
00:38:38,970 --> 00:38:40,490
I just saw my sister.

603
00:38:40,890 --> 00:38:42,490
She's looking for you.

604
00:39:02,890 --> 00:39:04,291
Is it fun to fool an honest man?

605
00:39:07,331 --> 00:39:08,371
It's more fun to fool you.

606
00:39:09,450 --> 00:39:10,490
Time will tell.

607
00:39:11,051 --> 00:39:12,490
Let's wait and see

608
00:39:12,771 --> 00:39:13,611
who is the winner.

609
00:39:15,410 --> 00:39:19,490
Good. Being a princess makes you bolder.

610
00:39:24,650 --> 00:39:26,011
You're so eager to see Tushan Jing.

611
00:39:27,051 --> 00:39:28,450
Why did you run away just now?

612
00:39:31,490 --> 00:39:32,690
How can I get out of this maze?

613
00:39:34,890 --> 00:39:37,771
There are many interesting things
to see in this maze now.

614
00:39:38,170 --> 00:39:39,051
Aren't you interested?

615
00:39:39,811 --> 00:39:40,450
For example,

616
00:39:41,450 --> 00:39:42,970
my sister and Tushan...

617
00:39:43,051 --> 00:39:43,490
No.

618
00:39:47,250 --> 00:39:48,571
Don't regret it then.

619
00:40:16,672 --> 00:40:18,170
I just played chess with Jing.

620
00:40:18,688 --> 00:40:19,851
Looks like I've lost.

621
00:40:20,611 --> 00:40:22,970
Cang Xuan, why don't you take my place?

622
00:40:23,371 --> 00:40:24,611
And I'll take Jing's place.

623
00:40:25,210 --> 00:40:26,531
Let's try turning the game around.

624
00:40:27,450 --> 00:40:28,250
Alright.

625
00:40:54,650 --> 00:40:55,136
Miss.

626
00:40:56,131 --> 00:40:56,851
What's the matter?

627
00:40:57,371 --> 00:40:58,690
Miss Zhan is not feeling well.

628
00:40:59,091 --> 00:41:00,611
Mr. Fan has taken her home first.

629
00:41:01,131 --> 00:41:01,771
Got it.

630
00:41:05,170 --> 00:41:07,291
Miss Zhan, Fan Zhang's fiancee?

631
00:41:08,250 --> 00:41:09,650
Who else could be?

632
00:41:10,410 --> 00:41:12,410
It is said the Zhan family
had a feud with Chi Chen

633
00:41:12,650 --> 00:41:13,890
and were wiped out.

634
00:41:14,170 --> 00:41:15,611
Now she is the only child left.

635
00:41:15,811 --> 00:41:17,091
Fortunately, the Fan family

636
00:41:17,091 --> 00:41:18,210
has been taking care of her.

637
00:41:21,170 --> 00:41:23,051
Chi Chen is the General of Chenrong,

638
00:41:24,011 --> 00:41:25,051
but after his death,

639
00:41:25,331 --> 00:41:27,072
no one in Central Plains mourned
for him.

640
00:41:28,490 --> 00:41:29,371
People should hate him.

641
00:41:30,170 --> 00:41:31,851
Chi Chen was brutal and violent,

642
00:41:32,011 --> 00:41:32,970
causing too many deaths.

643
00:41:34,450 --> 00:41:36,170
Everyone can curse Chi Chen,

644
00:41:37,170 --> 00:41:39,051
except the Chenrong family.

645
00:41:47,650 --> 00:41:49,531
Tell me why.

646
00:41:51,331 --> 00:41:53,011
You should ask your father about this.

647
00:41:54,611 --> 00:41:57,730
You will find out

648
00:41:58,531 --> 00:42:00,331
which side is indebted.

649
00:42:01,250 --> 00:42:01,930
Fangfeng Bei.

650
00:42:05,930 --> 00:42:06,690
What's going on?

651
00:42:12,250 --> 00:42:13,091
Miss Fangfeng,

652
00:42:13,890 --> 00:42:15,051
