658
00:42:30,650 --> 00:42:32,611
You do it yourself.

659
00:42:33,851 --> 00:42:35,771
You're not married
into the Tushan family yet.

660
00:42:36,851 --> 00:42:37,811
Don't consider yourself

661
00:42:38,210 --> 00:42:40,291
