675
00:43:42,976 --> 00:43:44,250
I will punish myself with three cups

676
00:43:44,571 --> 00:43:45,690
as an apology to you.

677
00:43:54,890 --> 00:43:55,571
She's my friend.

678
00:43:56,490 --> 00:43:58,210
It's normal to argue.

679
00:43:59,091 --> 00:44:00,051
If I take it to heart,

680
00:44:00,371 --> 00:44:01,611
I will be petty.

681
00:44:02,811 --> 00:44:03,771
Thank you, Miss Fangfeng.

682
00:44:09,970 --> 00:44:10,730
So sweet.

683
00:44:15,611 --> 00:44:16,851
Xiaoyao and I will leave first.

684
00:44:17,730 --> 00:44:19,170
Let's get together another time.

685
